Insider Activity


Individual




Joseph A. Plomin



Mr. Joseph A. Plomin is President-Europe & Asia Pacific Region at Meritor, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Automotive Axles Ltd. and Heavy Duty Manufacturers Association.
Mr. Plomin was previously employed as an Product Manager by Federal Signal Corp. and SVP-Sales, Marketing & Product Line Management by Remy Holdings, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Knox College.



